cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the performance of complex-valued neural networks on real-valued classification tasks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of complex numbers in neural networks also has applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the handling of noise, which is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI).
